    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><b>Monitoring:</b></td>
    <td>
      <ul>
        <li>I will respond to requests from PREVENT-AD, if any. I will immediately report to PREVENT-AD activity that breaches these terms.</li>
      </ul>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
